125
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] A legendarno, 41.

126
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da.

127
00:10:58,000 --> 00:11:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] 45. on nas vraća.

128
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:11,000
