140
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bili smo u, tamo smo prespavili, onda smo došli u opatiju, to je malo bliže.

141
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da.

142
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sisku od...

143
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:31,000
