323
00:32:48,000 --> 00:32:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali nešto mora biti u stanju same, proizumen.

324
00:32:51,000 --> 00:32:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je strašno da mi toliko hrane uvozimo.

325
00:32:53,000 --> 00:32:54,000
