365
00:35:14,000 --> 00:35:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ja sam bio sa...

366
00:35:17,000 --> 00:35:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bio sam, znači kao novinar,

367
00:35:19,000 --> 00:35:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] u nekom trenutku sam radio i kao fikser.

368
00:35:22,000 --> 00:35:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Fikser je osoba koja dogovara za strane ekipe,

369
00:35:26,000 --> 00:35:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] nekakve termine i tako i u...

370
00:35:29,000 --> 00:35:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kada smo ulazili u Europsku uniju, znači u 2013.

371
00:35:33,000 --> 00:35:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Javila mi se...

372
00:35:35,000 --> 00:35:39,000
