374
00:35:42,000 --> 00:35:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] i snimatelj nizozemoc je primijetio da...

375
00:35:45,000 --> 00:35:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Puno ljudi šeta i...

376
00:35:48,000 --> 00:35:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da kažemo...

377
00:35:50,000 --> 00:35:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dangubi po...

378
00:35:51,000 --> 00:35:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da.

379
00:35:52,000 --> 00:35:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to nije njihovo.

380
00:35:53,000 --> 00:35:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači...

381
00:35:54,000 --> 00:35:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mora postati neko vodstvo kompanije koje je u stanju...

382
00:35:58,000 --> 00:36:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pronaći posle, osmisliti posle i...

383
00:36:00,000 --> 00:36:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

384
00:36:01,000 --> 00:36:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, na krajnjoj liniji ti ljudi su zato i bolje...

385
00:36:04,000 --> 00:36:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zato su direktori i bolje plaćeni.

386
00:36:06,000 --> 00:36:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno.

387
00:36:07,000 --> 00:36:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali...

388
00:36:08,000 --> 00:36:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi imamo...

389
00:36:09,000 --> 00:36:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, to sad filozofirati...

390
00:36:11,000 --> 00:36:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nosi jednu dasku u kruk ko onove...

391
00:36:14,000 --> 00:36:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

392
00:36:15,000 --> 00:36:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne ide to, ne ide, da.

393
00:36:16,000 --> 00:36:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, da.

394
00:36:17,000 --> 00:36:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zorislav, šta je najteže u borbi patri korupcije?

395
00:36:20,000 --> 00:36:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ili vama bilo sustav, ljudi, anodušnost?

396
00:36:24,000 --> 00:36:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, prvo...

397
00:36:25,000 --> 00:36:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prvo...

398
00:36:27,000 --> 00:36:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imamo par pro...

399
00:36:28,000 --> 00:36:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad je reč o korupciji, znači, samo dvije stvari su sigurne.

400
00:36:32,000 --> 00:36:35,000
